<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.4">
<l>evvam vevvēl poṉpeyarō ṉētala ṉiṉṉuyirai vavvi yākam vaḷḷukirāl vakirntavam māṉatiṭam</l>
<l>kavvu nāyuṅ kaḻukumucci pōtoṭu kālcuḻaṉṟu</l>
<l>teyva mallāl cellavoṇṇāc ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of [our] lord, who sliced with sharp claws the chest of his enemy,</l>
<l>Whose name was “gold” [with] a distressing cruel spear,</l>
<l rend="indent">snatching away [his] life,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain, impossible to traverse, except by the gods,</l>
<l>[With] snapping dogs, hawks, and winds circling at high noon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
